{"tid":1548373,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」被捕時有乜方法可以即時向外界透露自己身分","createTime":"2019-09-07T04:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:15:31.000Z","uid":147671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"879e8fa6e3056ae888680824274fa9af7784fbc8","tid":1548373,"uid":147671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因最近太多疑似被自殺案件<br />\n而當被捕人士被捕時，狗都用不同方式使記者聽唔到義士名稱，導致被捕無名無姓嘅義士處境十分危險<br />\n<br />\n所以如果於被捕時，及未被沒收通訊器材能秒速通知姓名、身分證就可以俾律師跟進</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落<br />\n一個不能少</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"3ea3ef612255298644caafe2c45192ec2a722b3a","tid":1548373,"uid":147671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:01:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f86485d19625e36a56e95a353461d8fab91f75b8","tid":1548373,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"好似上次巴士咁，可以用手勢打中文電碼？（身份證上面）"},{"pid":"977b5220fcbb513be27f108659aac6512a30fa5c","tid":1548373,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實可以扮暈訓低不停叫要去醫院"},{"pid":"b04f71b4b5eb5c6d73577be14a978ef6212aa6d4","tid":1548373,"uid":147671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"有無啲器材係按一個掣，人地就即知姓名身分證？"},{"pid":"c957482a2095447be9a990016c6115fb004f72a5","tid":1548373,"uid":147671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"977b5220fcbb513be27f108659aac6512a30fa5c","tid":1548373,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實可以扮暈訓低不停叫要去醫院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"如果環境係趕走曬記者，你暈嘅話啲狗應該唔理你"},{"pid":"fe5aad9272529455a343ff307b58245a9e5492e5","tid":1548373,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c957482a2095447be9a990016c6115fb004f72a5","tid":1548373